{"tid":1641720,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］燒山挑戰誠哥！？","createTime":"2019-10-09T12:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T04:17:59.000Z","uid":175453,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"deed894ea5ab443f71234d14a36db6f8906a5103","tid":1641720,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:21:24.000Z","msg":"燒山係尋日（10月8）燈左我地一獲，話我地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">難以潰散</span></span><br />\n姐係示威者又好易收皮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jvpU7EGyk8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjvpU7EGyk8A&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNo6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=222d03e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jvpU7EGyk8A</a><br />\n<br />\n而眾所週知，誠哥上知天文 下知地理，全世界都認為佢有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">預測未來</span></span>既能力。<br />\n而最近，誠哥不斷挑中共機<br />\n例如：<br />\n收中共企業數<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/09/25/a102672490.html/amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2019%2F09%2F25%2Fa102672490.html%2Famp&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNo6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=e27cd919\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/09/25/a102672490.html/amp</a><br />\n又如：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2019-09-19/70525212\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2019-09-19%2F70525212&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNo6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=e0540332\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2019-09-19/70525212</a><br />\n<br />\n種種事蹟表明誠哥同中共係到明爭暗鬥，而做到呢步明顯係預測到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">即使硬碰硬</span></span>對佢既利益係大於損失。暗示示威者最終能獲勝。<br />\n<br />\n而家問題黎啦，燒山既燈力接近百分百準確，而誠哥預測未來既能力令佢成為首富。咁到底香港人既未來會係點？<br />\n<br />\n誠哥預測未來未衰過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n燒山燈完實中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6508141ac87f540e939c92a6e8f758f728c74a8e","tid":1641720,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:22:40.000Z","msg":"另類連儂牆 家家戶戶都知道<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1641528\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1641528</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"13591daf9d6785451cda563fbdeff0a4a16fbb57","tid":1641720,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:22:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3096b023f900a191baf2909303550dcab811e70","tid":1641720,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:22:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"953add3f3a2f6eb3a279afc1e90dc03e6709d2a2","tid":1641720,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:23:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"105d2cdde2d0f1f08a5767afa46310715a01d668","tid":1641720,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:24:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d00c64ceea5b48e180085d43c1f91b0eedae4f12","tid":1641720,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:24:31.000Z","msg":"邊個負皮"},{"pid":"6d33204809dbd129153f093759d54d762b32d6a3","tid":1641720,"uid":5674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:25:01.000Z","msg":"矛盾大對決！"},{"pid":"9424ea5c3c179529d8e4e3287de7728cb9aea2e6","tid":1641720,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d33204809dbd129153f093759d54d762b32d6a3","tid":1641720,"uid":5674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:25:01.000Z","msg":"矛盾大對決！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:25:30.000Z","msg":"點算"},{"pid":"da87a530